Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:02.68,Date & Time,Sign,0,0,0,,Akasaka, PM 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:02.72,Date & Time,Sign,0,0,0,,Akasaka, PM 10
